{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1473985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "g（x）的xe^x写成e^（x+lnx）再用放缩", "timestamp": 1618671770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474007, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "江苏卷的Bob看着Alice一愣，才想起来全国卷可以放缩。。。我的话会使尽全身解数规避放缩，因为会扣分。", "timestamp": 1618672023, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是2e-1吗？这样代入x等于1就不对呀", "timestamp": 1618672183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "也可以不放苏欧，注意g'=0等价于一个递增函数在两个点取到同一个值，于是这两个点重合", "timestamp": 1618672304, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 貌似答案是2e-1，没太明白…，放缩是把lnx放成x-1吗", "timestamp": 1618672399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474123, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "W函数\n", "timestamp": 1618673010, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474827, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "九字班路过，这题我高考之前做过，，，答案应该是小于1\n", "timestamp": 1618678647, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474841, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一个挺经典的隐零点题了吧\n零点应该是在x*e^x=1取到（无解析解对于高中生来讲是比较坑的）", "timestamp": 1618678753, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474872, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 289192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, 